//Data level

创建mogodb:
  0. cd ~/mongodb-osx-x86_64-3.2.4
  1. cd bin
  2. mkdir -p data/db
  3. mkdir log/
  4. touch credit_loan

启动mongodb:
  4. ./mongod --dbpath=../data/db/ --logpath ../log/credit_loan --fork
测试启动是否正常:
  5. ./mongo
  6. use credit_loan
  7. db.users.save({name:'002233',password:123456})
  8. 27017

